name: Ep136: Dan Moore by The Geek Within
summary:
Today's guest is Dan Moore. He is the head of Devrel at FusionAuth and the author of "Letters To A New Developer", which is subtitled, What I Wish I Had Known When Starting My Development Career.

Episode 136 on YouTube: https://youtu.be/1C1q-o6DtPU

You can engage Dan here:
LinkedIn - https://www.linkedin.com/in/mooreds/
Website - https://letterstoanewdeveloper.com/
Book - https://www.amazon.com/Letters-New-Developer-Starting-Development-ebook/dp/B08FD7DG943
Substack - https://ciamweekly.substack.com

The Geek Within can be found on several podcast platforms - https://www.polywork.com/posts/W0IZQ1lu

List of past episodes: https://tgwlink.net/episodes
